      "format": "3s",
      "surface": "grass",
      "description": "Trilogy Triples Coed — a Saturday coed 3s tournament on grass from FVBL (@fvbleague), the Bay Area grass series based in the Newark/Fremont area. Sign up through the bit.ly RSVP — that form, not the FB event, is what gets you on the team list. Triples plays on the shorter (2s) court at men's net height. Standard FVBL hand rules apply: no open-hand passing on serve receive or rallies (open hand only on hard-driven hits), set-overs allowed only on 2nd/3rd touch and must be square, blocks don't count as a touch, no rotation fault but serve order must be maintained, lets are live, one service attempt. Format is pool play into a playoff bracket with one timeout per set, 5-minute warmups, late penalties after 10 minutes and forfeit at 20. Teams BYO whistle for reffing and BYO ball, shade, food, and water."
    },
